title: PPPP’s Haji Rasool Bakhsh Chandio wins NA-223 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarian candidate Haji Rasool Bakhsh Chandio has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-223 Badin-II by securing 1,15,681 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Grand Democratic Alliance candidate Muhammad Hassam Mirza, who bagged 79,152 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 49.75 percent.
